0.9.4.name: wordpress/swedish-greys
0.9.4.description: A blog style WordPress theme inspired by the Swedish design era Swedish grace (1910-1930), the subtle nuances of the grey scale and clean typography. The theme includes 7 widgetized areas, Theme Options Panel, layout on per post/page basis, full Localisation Support - Swedish, Russian and Romanian translation included. Support forum at http://nordicthemepark.com/forums/.
